Feature: Hotel Booking In Adactin Application

@Ad1
Scenario: Login Functionality

Given user Launch The Application

When user Enter The "<Username>" In Username Field

And user Enter The "<Password>" In Password Field

Then user Click On The Login Button And It Navigates To The Search Hotel Page

Examples:
|Username|Password|
|ABCD|1233|
|XYZ|1222|
|softtester|adc@123|

@Ad1
Scenario: Search Hotel

When user Select The "London" In Location Field

And user Select The "Hotel Sunshine" In Hotels Field

And user Select The "Super Deluxe" In Room Type Field

And user Select The "10" In Number OF Rooms Field

And user Enter The "15/10/2022" In Check In Date Field

And user Enter The "25/10/2022" In Check Out Date Field

And user Select The "2 - Two" In Adults Per Room Field

And user Select The 1 In Children Per Room Field

Then user Click On The Search Button And It Navigates To The Select Hotel Page

@Ad1
Scenario: Select Hotel

When user Click On the Radio Button To Select Hotel

Then user Click On The Continue Button And It Navigates To The Book A Hotel Page

@Ad1
Scenario: Book A Hotel
 
When user Enter The "AAA" In First Name Field

And user Enter The "BBB" In Last Name Field

And user Enter The "xxx" In Billing Address Field

And user Enter The "1234123412341234" In Credit Card No. Field

And user Select The "VISA" In Credit Card Type Field

And user Select The 10 and "2022" In Expiry Date Field

And user Enter The "234" In CVV Number Field

Then user Click On The Book Now Button And HoTel Booking Is Taken Place 